description:
Make your friends laugh with several great free sound effects
Make your friends laugh with four great free sound effects! Includes rimshot (ba-dum-tss), sad trombone (wah-wah-wah), crickets, and "nope". More sound effects are on the way!

This app has been originally written by Brian Nezvadovitz and published on GitHub. It was modified by Andrej and now Tyler.
